<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">由于</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">IA公司能够提供20年付款保终身的儿童重疾产品，因此在儿童重疾险领域，其市场占有率一直稳居全加拿大第一。由于价格便宜，不少家长都是在孩子一出生即购买儿童重疾险产品。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: SimSun;">成人重疾险和儿童重疾险产品的差异</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.6pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">成人重疾险和儿童重疾险主要的区别在于：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.6pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #ffa900;">相同保额下保费不同：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.6pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">年龄越小保费越低，因此越早买越划算。以</span><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">IA公司的重疾险产品为例，1岁孩子保障10万，20年付完，男孩每月保费91元，女孩每月保费88元。而45岁成人同样保障10万，20年付完，男士每月保费330元，女士每月保费290元。不仅主险保费差异明显，就连保费退还附加条款的保费差异也非常明显。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.6pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #ffa900;">保障病种不同：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.6pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">通常成人重疾险保障</span><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">25项重大疾病（癌症、心脏病和中风是加拿大人最容易诱发的重大疾病，其他22项重大疾病包含：冠状动脉搭桥手术、后天性脑损伤、老人痴呆症、主动脉手术、再生障碍性贫血、良性脑瘤、细菌性脑膜炎、失明、昏迷、失聪、心瓣置换、肾衰竭、肢体截肢、丧失语言能力、主要器官移植、等候替换已衰竭的主要器官、运动神经元疾病、多发性硬化、工伤感染HIV、瘫痪、帕金森症、严重烧伤）</span></p>
<p style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.6pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">而儿童重疾险在成人重疾险的保障病种基础之上，会增加一型糖尿病</span><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">TYPE 1 DIABETES MELLITUS、纤维化囊肿CYSTIC FIBROSIS、肌肉萎缩MUSCULAR DYSTROPHY、大脑瘫痪CEREBRAL PALSY、先天性心脏病CONGENITAL HEART DISEASE、唐氏综合症DOWN SYNDROME等。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.6pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #ffa900;">体检要求不同：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.6pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">儿童无需体检，成人根据保额和年龄需要体检，而且重疾险的体检标准比较高。尤其是对</span><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">45岁以后的成人，体检要求更高。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: SimSun;">儿童重疾险配置是家庭刚需</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">儿童重疾险的配置是家庭刚需，特别是在加拿大。其原因在于：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">1.加拿大公费医疗效率低下，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #00d100;">等待公费医疗容易延误孩子救治最佳时机</span></strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">2.加拿大重疾险产品都是可以设置保费退还的，相当于用保费的利息为孩子做了一份保障。而加拿大整体金融环境一直处于低利率的状态，用最少的钱给孩子带来终身的保障是明智之举。简单来讲，每月100元左右的预算，缴费20年，保障10万，假设利息3%，相当于每年1000-1200元本金的利息，<strong><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;">即</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;">30-36元的利息（还需缴税）给孩子做了一份10万元重疾险的保障。</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #00d100;">换句话说，也就是每天</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #00d100;">1毛钱，换来10万元的保障！！！</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">3.加拿大重疾险保费一直在涨价中，唯一涨幅比较少的是儿童重疾险，我们在此做个大胆预测，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #00d100;">儿童重疾险的价格肯定会涨，甚至是付款</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #00d100;">20年保终身的产品会渐渐淡出市场</span></strong><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #a1a1a1;">，到时想申请都无法申请到，因为保险公司承担的风险实在是太高了！</span></p>